-- UniCredit Investor CRT Will Review Profumo's Performance, Corriere Says
-- Alessandra Migliaccio
-- 2010-09-20T06:09:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-20/unicredit-investor-crt-will-review-profumo-s-performance-corriere-says.html

          
          
             UniCredit SpA  investor Fondazione
CRT wants to review the performance of Chief Executive Officer
 Alessandro Profumo  at the bank’s next shareholder meeting, CRT
Chairman  Andrea Comba  told Corriere della Sera.  
 The meeting will offer the opportunity to verify whether
Profumo’s management of the bank has been “in line with our
interests,” Comba said in an interview published in the
newspaper’s weekly business section.  
